schedule.text:
Desiring to make provision for the reciprocal
            surrender of fugitive
            offenders;

Recalling the rights conferred on every
            person involved in criminal proceedings in accordance with generally recognised
            standards;

subparagraph.content:
as accurate a description as possible of the fugitive offender, together
                    with any other information which would help to establish his identity,
                    nationality and, if known, his whereabouts;

any other offence for which surrender may be granted under this Agreement
                    in respect of which the requested Party may consent to his being dealt
                    with;
